  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“If you would take a man’s life, you owe it to him to look into his eyes and hear his final words. And if you cannot bear to do that, then perhaps the man does not deserve to die.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot113.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot113.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot113.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot113.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_1\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 1\">Chapter 1</a>, Bran I, 13.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403123242\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 51/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8424/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 296/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 25/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 454/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    3.885      1 -total\n100.00%    3.885      1 Template:Ref\n 62.80%    2.440      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:2462-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403123242 and revision id 217766\n -->\n",
